    "description": {
      "value": "<p><span style=\"font-family:Lexend,sans-serif\">You use mental suggestions on your brain to convince your body it is capable of continuing. You gain 3d6 temporary hit points. While you have these temporary hit points, you have advantage on saving throws to end physical conditions on yourself.</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Lexend,sans-serif\"><strong>Upcast: </strong>For each rank you cast this jutsu above D-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3 and the temporary hit points by 1d6.</span></p>",
